1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,680
Ngifuna ukukubonisa ukuthi ungacwaninga kanjani noma yini ngoba ucwaningo lunamandla.

2
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:10,000
Kubuye kube ikhono futhi uma usufundile ukuthi ungakwenza kanjani, ungazifundisa ngokoqobo

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,000
noma yini oyifunayo.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,760
Futhi uma siqaphela muva nje ukuthi abantu abaningi abazi ukuthi bangacwaninga kanjani, bayazi ukuthi

5
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:15,760
ukufuna.

6
00:00:15,760 --> 00:00:19,880
Futhi empeleni kunomehluko omkhulu kakhulu ngoba uma usesha, uthembela kwabanye

7
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,440
abantu ukuba bacabange ngawe futhi asifuni lokho.

8
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,840
Sifuna ukwenza kangcono.

9
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:26,080
Ngakho-ke, ucwaningo lunezigaba zalo.

10
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:29,560
Isistimu yami engiyisebenzisayo inezinombolo ezine, ngakho ngizokuqondisa kuzo.

11
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:31,680
Esinye siwukudinga kwakho indawo.

12
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:35,600
Yilapho okudingeka uqale khona, kodwa futhi yilapho abantu abaningi beyeka khona.

13
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:41,760
Lokhu ukusesha kwakho ku-Google, amavidiyo we-TikTok, izincazelo ze-YouTube, izimpendulo ze-AI.

14
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:46,519
Futhi inkinga yokuma lapha ukuthi uthola iziphetho ezicindezelwayo futhi

15
00:00:46,519 --> 00:00:48,640
bengakuqondi ukuthi zakhiwa kanjani.

16
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,640
Ngakho ake sithathe isibonelo.

17
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:55,000
Ake sithi ucwaninga ukuthi yini into emnyama futhi uthola imiphumela efana,

18
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:57,600
ihlanganisa u-85% wendawo yonke.

19
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,760
Asikwazi ukuyibona.

20
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:00,520
Ithinta amandla adonsela phansi.

21
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:05,120
Uthola wonke la maqiniso, kodwa namanje awuqondi izinto ezinjengokuthi sazi kanjani ukuthi

22
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:11,440
Ingabe ikhona noma yibuphi ubufakazi obuwusekelayo noma yiziphi izimfundiso ezincintisanayo?

23
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,480
Ngakho-ke, ungayibeka kanjani kahle i-level one?

24
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:17,400
Uyisebenzisa njengendlela yokuziqondisa hhayi njengendlela yokufundisa.

25
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:23,560
Ngakho-ke umgomo wakho kuleli zinga kufanele ube ukufunda amagama, ukukhomba imiqondo esemqoka

26
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:27,760
futhi uzenzele imibuzo eminingi, uthole ukuthi yini osaziyo futhi

27
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,920
okuyinto wena namanje ngempela ufuna ukwazi.

28
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:34,800
Cishe uchitha imizuzu engu-10 kuya kwengu-15 ucwaninga ezingeni lokuqala.

29
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:39,000
Khona-ke uyama futhi uzibuze, yini engingayiqondi?

30
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:42,160
Futhi lowo mbuzo uyindlela yakho eya ezingeni lakho lesibili.

31
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,760
Izinga lesibili ukwandisa umthombo.

32
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:47,160
Yilapho uqala khona ukuhlola ngempela.

33
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,760
Ngakho lokhu kubukeka kanjani?

34
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:51,880
Lokhu ukuchofoza emithonjeni nasezihlokweni.

35
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:55,520
Kufundwa izifundo eziphelele esikhundleni nje sokufingqa isifundo.

36
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:59,120
Landela izixhumanisi, izingcaphuno nezinkomba.

37
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,520
Yilapho uya khona.

38
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,520
Kuyini lokhu?

39
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,520
Kwavelaphi lokhu?

40
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,680
Ake sibuyele esibonelweni sezinto ezimnyama.

41
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,640
Manje awusahlali ku-Google noma ku-TikTok.

42
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:10,759
Uvula ikhasi leNASA.

43
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,640
Uchofoza ocwaningweni olukhonjiwe.

44
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:18,520
Uvula i-Galaxy Rotation Curve Study futhi ubona ukubonwa ngu

45
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,520
ososayensi.

46
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:24,400
Ngakho lokhu kubaluleke kakhulu ngoba manje ubona ubufakazi hhayi nje isiphetho.

47
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:28,080
Ngakho-ke, uyivula kanjani yonke into ngendlela efanele?

48
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,640
Musa nje ukufunda ikhasi bese ulivala.

49
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:33,600
Kufanele ube namathebu amahlanu kuya kwayishumi avulekile kukho konke okubukayo.

50
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,400
Kufanele ulandele izingcaphuno emuva ngalesi sikhathi.

51
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:41,760
Ngakho kusukela esihlokweni kuya ocwaningweni kuya kwedatha yokuqala, konke lokho kuhle ngaso sonke isikhathi

52
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,760
zihlobene kakhulu.

53
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:49,760
Kufanele ubeke phambili.edu's.gov's, amaphepha eshicilelwe, noma yikuphi okuqukethwe okuvela uchwepheshe

54
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,760
insimu.

55
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:56,000
Futhi kufanele uzibuze, uyini lo mbono engifuna ukuwusekela?

56
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,799
Ngoba uma ungakwazi ukuphendula lokho, cishe usesezingeni lokuqala.

57
00:02:59,799 --> 00:03:02,959
Ngiya ezingeni lesithathu, okuwukubona amaphethini.

58
00:03:02,959 --> 00:03:07,519
Futhi ngicabanga ukuthi leli yizinga lapho iqiniso liqala ngempela ukuvela ngoba

59
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:13,040
kuleli zinga, ukugxila kwakho okuyinhloko ukuqhathanisa imithombo eminingi futhi unake

60
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:16,000
ukuvumelana nokuphikisana phakathi kwabo.

61
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,880
Ubona imibono ephindaphindiwe.

62
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:25,200
Ufuna ngempela izinto ezivela ngokuphindaphindiwe kulezo zinsiza, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi

63
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:31,480
izinombolo noma imibuzo noma imibono noma izimpikiswano ngoba kubonisa ukuthi zibalulekile.

64
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:35,160
Ake sithi ufunda imithombo eyisithupha ehlukene ngezinto ezimnyama.

65
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:39,359
Futhi eziyisithupha kubo bathi ukujikeleza Galaxy akufani mass ebonakalayo futhi omunye wabo

66
00:03:39,359 --> 00:03:41,800
wathi mhlawumbe imithetho yokudonsela phansi ayilungile.

67
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:46,280
Ngakho manje uyabona ngempela ukuthi ukuvumelana kwenzeka ngaphakathi kwesihloko uqobo.

68
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:51,240
Uma ubona ama-outliers futhi ubona impikiswano ekhona futhi uqala ukuthola real

69
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,280
ukuqonda lokho okufundayo.

70
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:56,720
Kunoma yiliphi izinga, ezintathu kahle, ufuna ukuhlangana.

71
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,000
Ngakho, imiphi imithombo evumelana ngayo?

72
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,640
Nawe kufanele uqaphele ukungaboni ngaso linye.

73
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:05,720
Ngakho cabanga ukuthi izazi ziyahlukaphi kule ndaba.

74
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,920
Kufanele uhlele ubufakazi obutholakalayo.

75
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:11,880
Ungayihlukanisa ibe ubufakazi obuqinile noma ukuqagela.

76
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:17,039
Ungase futhi udale njengamabhakede amathathu engqondo noma ubhale phansi uma ufuna kusobala.

77
00:04:17,039 --> 00:04:22,039
Kodwa enye imininingwane oyitholayo iyavumelana kuyo yonke imithombo.

78
00:04:22,039 --> 00:04:27,680
Olunye ulwazi oluphikiswana ngalo nolunye ulwazi olungaqinisekile.

79
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:32,020
Futhi ngokwenza lokho, empeleni uzifundisa futhi wakhe ubuhlakani bakho

80
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,720
isahlulelo esiphathelene nale ndaba.

81
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:38,960
A ezingeni ukujula kanye nohlaka ezingeni ngoba lapha lapho uyeka ukufunda ulwazi

82
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:41,800
bese uqala ukucabanga ngezinhlelo.

83
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,520
Ubuza imibuzo engcono.

84
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:48,400
Uyakha amamodeli engqondo endabeni oyicwaningayo futhi uqala

85
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:52,800
ukuxhuma imibono emikhakheni ehlukene yocwaningo.

86
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:58,000
Ngakho-ke ufuna ngempela ukwakheka ngemuva kwesihloko salokho okucwaninga ngakho.

87
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:02,680
Esikhundleni sokubuza ukuthi yini into emnyama, sibuza imibuzo ejulile.

88
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:08,000
Sibuza izinto ezinjengokuthi kungani amandla adonsela phansi aziphatha ngale ndlela noma yiziphi izibikezelo ezakhiwe

89
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:13,480
kumodeli yethu ekhona yendaba emnyama noma lokho okudingeka kube yiqiniso kukho konke lokhu

90
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,480
ukuba abe engalungile.

91
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:20,360
Uziqeqesha ngempela ukuba ucabange ngokujulile futhi ubuze imibuzo engcono,

92
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,360
ibaluleke kakhulu ocwaningweni.

93
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:27,880
Izinga esibuza ngalo imibuzo yesibili, asibuzi nje ukuthi yini, kodwa kungani futhi

94
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:31,160
kuthiwani uma sakha phezu kwamamodeli ethu engqondo.

95
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:34,120
Ngakho thatha ucezu lwephepha bese uludweba phambi kwakho, akunjalo?

96
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:37,120
Indaba emnyama, iyindawo yokulahlekelwa izibalo.

97
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,000
Kutholakala ngemiphumela yokudonsela phansi.

98
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,200
Akubonakali ngokuqondile.

99
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:44,920
Dweba ukuze ubone imephu bese uqala ukuyixhumanisa.

100
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,080
Indaba emnyama iyisifundo sezinto eziphilayo.

101
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,240
Kuyinto cosmology.

102
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,280
Kuyinto ifilosofi yesayensi.

103
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:54,960
Ungathatha ulwazi onalo bese uludonsela ebufakazini, obungaqinisekile,

104
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:58,559
ukuthi yini mayelana nesihloko ukulinganiselwa kolwazi lwethu.

105
00:05:58,559 --> 00:06:02,599
Lapho uqala ukukudweba phambi kwakho futhi wakhe imodeli ukuthi uqala ukubona

106
00:06:02,599 --> 00:06:06,320
zonke izixhumanisi futhi uqala ukubona zonke izikhala ezingekho.

107
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:10,159
Futhi kuyahlanya ukuthi lokho kusiza kangakanani ekuqondeni kwakho.

108
00:06:10,159 --> 00:06:13,599
Into nge ucwaningo wukuthi akuyona linear, kuyinto loop.

109
00:06:13,599 --> 00:06:17,719
Ngakho usesha bese wandisa bese uqhathanisa bese wakha lezo zengqondo

110
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,720
onobuhle.

111
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,240
Futhi kulawo mamodeli engqondo uthola imibuzo engcono.

112
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:25,640
Futhi bese uyiphindaphinda yonke futhi ngemibuzo engcono oyifunayo futhi wandisa

113
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,680
uphinde uqhathanise futhi wakhe amamodeli amaningi.

114
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,720
Futhi yilapho ufunda khona ukucabanga ngokwakho.

115
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:34,680
Yilapho uqala khona ngempela ukuqonda okuthile.

116
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:39,000
Futhi yilokho okwenza ukulandela ukwazi kwakho kube namandla kakhulu.

